MUST READ!
Change <nominal>80</nominal> to the amount of spawns you have within cfgeventspawns. 
Change <min>45</min> to the minimum of nodes you want to spawn in (Can not be the same for nominal) so do 5 less.  
Change <max>85</max> to the maximun of nodes you want to spawn in (Can do 5 over nominal or same number).

Do this for all of them (MUST CHANGE):
<child lootmax="0" lootmin="0" max="8" min="5" type="FreezeNode_copper"/>
max="8" = Maximun of nodes 
min="5" = Mnimum of nodes

Information:
<lifetime>7200</lifetime> = How Long the node will stay there if no one mines it
<restock>800</restock> = If someone mines the node how long will it take to spawn back in

--- Copy From Here --
<event name="ItemNode">
    <nominal>80</nominal>
    <min>45</min>
    <max>85</max>
    <lifetime>7200</lifetime>
    <restock>800</restock>
    <saferadius>200</saferadius>
